# Simplified Academic Reader Implementation

The library reader has been streamlined to provide a clean, distraction-free scholarly experience by removing complex sidebars and additional modules.

## Key Changes
- **Simplified Focus**: Stripped redundant sidebars (Study Tools, High Yield Facts) to prioritize the document text.
- **Notion-style TOC**: Implemented a minimalist, high-speed Table of Contents for Markdown documents.
    - **Fast Access**: Hierarchy-aware navigation (H1, H2, H3) for clinical manuals.
    - **Hierarchical Styling**: Indented, clean typography mirroring modern knowledge management tools.
- **Focused Layout**: The content area is now centered and optimized for long-form reading.

